text: I am infuriated by non-voting stays. Don't they really understand that love alone is VERY MUCH NOT enough. No one gives desana for beautiful eyes, does not take ambassadors, and certainly does not allocate a huge budget for clips. Do they want to return to the District 9 era? For clips with two images and locations and with 0 graphics and special effects? So let's not do anything and we'll get back to where we started very quickly. But it's a pity for the guys that all their hard work and efforts, all the sleepless nights are going to hell. Because it's too difficult for someone to pick up a phone that I'm 100% sure won't let go of their hands and watch a freaking advertisement, at least an hour a day. In the same hour, you can safely collect 100 tickets, and if the advertising goes well, then all 200. We're collecting these damn tickets from DECEMBER 8th, until the end of voting - that's 41 days. This is 4100 without strain, and in the best case, all 8200. This is a huge help for the final vote. But no, we'll watch the edits, drool, write obscene comments, and on winning some nomination we'll write: "Well, my, well, handsome." No one asks us to sit in this khuzfan for days, one fucking hour a day, not to watch tt, but to watch ads. it's not difficult. Just laziness. "And why? There are a lot of them, they can handle it without me." And on the next loss: "Damn, it's a shame that we didn't win." I can't bring myself to name such consumers - stay.
